author: @LiSAAidorudaisuki
text:
Haerin is someone who strives for perfection in everything she does before sharing it with the world. With her calm and composed demeanor, she is a person of few words but great impact. Every word she speaks is thoughtfully considered, which might make her seem distant at times, but in reality, she is deeply sincere and true to herself.

Her performance of Automatic by Hikaru Utada highlighted her dedication. Despite never studying Japanese, she sang fluently with a natural accent. Likewise, her rendition of Ceiling by Lizzy McAlpine, with its challenging English lyrics and demanding high notes, showcased her growth and unique interpretation. Both performances were deeply impressive and reflected her continuous development.

Kang Haerinâ€™s charm lies in her captivating mystery, always waiting to be uncovered. She is like an ever-filling glass, constantly seeking ways to grow and embrace new opportunities. She never ceases to amaze.

Letâ€™s continue to support our girls wholeheartedly, every step of the way, until the very end.

#NewJeansNeverDie
